cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is about object tracking for unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves online learning and optimization, which suggests that it may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves processing video frames, which is a common task in multimedia (cs.MM).
